         <abstract>
            <p>This note presents nearly-best rational approximations for the functions &lt;tex-math&gt;$\operatorname{erf} (x)$&lt;/tex-math&gt; and &lt;tex-math&gt;$\operatorname{erfc} (x)$&lt;/tex-math&gt;, with maximal relative errors ranging down to between 6 × 10&lt;sup&gt;-19&lt;/sup&gt; and 3 × 10&lt;sup&gt;-20&lt;/sup&gt;.</p>
          </abstract>
